  <h3 id="editor-opencode">OpenCode</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>Open or create <code>~/.config/opencode/opencode.json</code> (global) or <code>opencode.json</code> in your project root:
      <pre><code># macOS / Linux:
mkdir -p ~/.config/opencode
nano ~/.config/opencode/opencode.json</code></pre>
    </li>
    <li>Add the MCP section:
      <pre><code>{`{
  "$schema": "https://opencode.ai/config.json",
  "mcp": {
    "lean-ctx": {
      "type": "local",
      "command": ["lean-ctx"],
      "enabled": true
    }
